{"tid":542600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【驚悚片】刀插後腦12小時　小李被射飛刀險死","createTime":"2018-01-27T15:48:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-28T01:53:08.000Z","uid":56533,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a7c136d74131e6ffc994d2cf228f206894d2bcce","tid":542600,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180127/640_b79df96a2cab0d5ce085f787a42f5b8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180127%2F640_b79df96a2cab0d5ce085f787a42f5b8c.jpg&h=0dceee48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國重慶綦江一名人稱「小李」的李姓男子，上周六（20日）與情敵爭執，被對方用飛刀插腦。過了近12個小時，他才到醫院就醫。<br />\n <br />\n小李表示，他在外打工認識一名女友，上周六他與情敵發生爭執，對方趁隨手就拿了一把8公分長的刀，插入他後腦。對方事後逃走，家人把他送到陸軍軍醫大學西南醫院搶救。<br />\n <br />\n負責治療的神經外科醫生李飛說，小李就診時，刀已在他腦內近12個小時，「雖然當時小李的意識非常清醒，但X光片顯示，刀片緊臨顱內重要血管。」經過近5小時的手術後，小李已脫離危險期，正在恢復中。<br />\n <br />\n李飛也感嘆小李「命大」，因為整把刀穿過他後腦勺的顱骨，橫貫小腦，刀尖離乙狀竇只有2公分，刀刃也僅離橫竇5公分，「這兩個竇是顱內最重要的靜脈，幾乎顱內所有的血液都通過它們回流到心臟，一旦被刀刺斷，會導致不可控制的大出血，那時後果將不堪設想。」（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180127/1286670/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180127%2F1286670%2F&d=TCECO9EFxHjleQyVYmg%2BMUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=9d5fe39c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180127%2F1286670%2F&h=6c2576dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180127/1286670/</a>"},{"pid":"92aa40069efe4ae71c65f7dc3d42ba2e72ff9716","tid":542600,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:52:20.000Z","msg":"李飞連醫生都撈埋"},{"pid":"87429639298f33fe73751297b48f6b2b2cb38071","tid":542600,"uid":124037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T15:53:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji